---
import SectionHeader from "@/common/components/astroComponentes/SectionHeader.astro";
import { Linkedin, Mail, Send } from "lucide-react";
---

<section
	id="contacto"
	class="sm:mx-auto mx-4 max-w-[32rem] py-8 sm:py-10 transition-all md:max-w-[42rem] lg:max-w-4xl"
>
	<div
		class="flex flex-col md:px-4 md:py-12 py-8 px-4 border rounded-md gap-6 items-center relative overflow-hidden
		       border-blue-300 dark:border-slate-600
		       bg-[conic-gradient(at_bottom_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-sky-100 via-sky-300 to-blue-400
		       dark:from-[#1d4ed8] dark:via-[#1e40af] dark:to-[#111827]
		       shadow-lg shadow-blue-300/50 dark:shadow-black/40
		       before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:w-full
		       before:h-full before:content-[''] before:opacity-[0.03] before:z-10 before:pointer-events-none
		       before:bg-[url('https://www.ui-layouts.com/noise.gif')]"
		data-reveal-item
		style="--motion-delay: 40ms; --motion-duration: var(--motion-duration-base); --motion-distance: 18px; --motion-blur: 4px;"
	>
		<div class="space-y-4">
			<SectionHeader title="Creemos algo juntos" center>
				<Send slot="icon" className="text-slate-900 dark:text-sky-300 h-8 w-8" />
			</SectionHeader>

			<p
				class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-300 md:text-base"
			>
				Abierto a nuevas oportunidades, colaboraciones freelance o simplemente para charlar sobre diseño, desarrollo y procesos creativos. Si tenés un proyecto en mente o querés conectar, este es un buen momento para hacerlo.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 items-center">
			<a
				href="mailto:matiasowjordan@gmail.com"
				target="_blank"
				class="gap-2 text-[16px] inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2.5 font-semibold text-center rounded-lg transition-all duration-200
				       bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white border border-slate-800
				       dark:bg-gray-900 dark:hover:bg-gray-950 dark:border-gray-700
				       shadow-md shadow-slate-900/25 dark:shadow-black/30
				       focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-white dark:focus-visible:ring-sky-500"
			>
				<Mail className="h-4 w-4" />
				Enviar correo
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
